Comment.val: /*fetches a list of all party's who possess the product (pprid) for a certain period of time*/

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT d.party_id , d.party_possession_perc, h.ppr_id , h.changedate FROM productpossession_hist_dt d, productpossession_hist_hd_vw h WHERE d.pphh_id =h.id AND h.ppr_id =~1 ORDER BY h.changedate, d.party_id

Text.val: Get most recent possession before change date
Get most recent possession before start date
Create initial possession on start date from previous possession.
Create possession on fiscal country change date from previous possession.
Create possession on product close date.
Create possession on change date from previous possession.
Create current possession using previous possession

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT f.party_id , f.changed_date, f.fiscal_country FROM fiscalcountry_per_party f WHERE f.changed_date BETWEEN to_date(':3', 'yyyymmdd') AND to_date(':2', 'yyyymmdd') AND f.party_id IN ( SELECT distinct d.party_id FROM productpossession_hist_dt d, productpossession_hist_hd_vw h WHERE d.pphh_id =h.id AND h.ppr_id = ~1 AND h.changedate <= to_date(':2', 'yyyymmdd'))

Text.val: Create current possession using previous possession

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT h.changedate FROM productpossession_hist_hd h WHERE h.ppr_id =~1 AND h.changedate <= to_date(':2', 'yyyymmdd') AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM productpossession_hist_dt d WHERE d.pphh_id=h.id)
